article_id:244,category_name:News,title_name:Flame-Attuned Adventurer Upgrade Event Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>The flame-attuned adventurer upgrade event is live as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550124000"></span>!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/6e53cb4869d22298c24b5d54bc1ef699.png"></div><div>The Flamehowl Ruins (Beginner/Standard/Expert) event quest, where you can obtain items for upgrading flame-attuned adventurers, is open for the duration of this event, and the Daily Bonus for Flamehowl Ruins is doubled.</div><div><br></div><div>But that&#39;s not all... The Daily Bonus for Flamehowl Ruins will be quadrupled when the 7-Day Pack (Double Bonus) is in effect! With all these bonuses, you&#39;ll really be cooking with fire!</div><div><br></div><div>â– Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550124000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550815199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>The schedule and content may change without warning.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1550124000,update_time1550123892